One of the best Caribbean eateries this side of Booklyn, food is good, presentation is good and service is good. With a focus on Guyanese cuisine, Bamboo Express provides food with an authentic 'back home' taste. The menu is vast and I can honestly say, everything is done well, try their chicken soup, fried rice (any kind ), curry chicken, jerk chicken or jerk pork. Their pastries or fried fish is to die for and if you've never had it ask for a bake and fish or a bag of poulouri...w/ tamarind sauce or pepper of course, enjoy n tell em Trry sent ya! Or say the guy with the big earings lolpwa
